# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Root .gitignore — ms-comm/ms-comm.github.io (GitHub Pages static site)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  This repository is served as a PUBLIC static site by GitHub Pages.
#  The `photo-server/` backend (Node.js + Express + admin panel + secrets)
#  is deployed SEPARATELY on Fly.io and MUST NOT be committed here — it
#  would both bloat the repo and expose admin surface / source code that
#  has no reason to be public.
#
#  Keep this file at the root; `photo-server/` also has its own
#  `.gitignore` that protects its local secrets (db/*.json, .env, …) in
#  case the folder is ever accidentally added to another repo.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Backend (deployed separately, never on GitHub Pages) ──────────────
photo-server/

# ── Environment / secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Node ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ── OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Editors ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── Build / cache ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
build/
.cache/
*.log
